### AI Support System - API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@conversationId = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 1. Create New Conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. List All Conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations

### 3. Get Specific Conversation Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/{{conversationId}}

### 4. Send Message - Simple
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}",
  "message": "Hello, how are you?"
}

### 5. Send Message - ORDER Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}",
  "message": "What's the status of my order #12345?"
}

### 6. Send Message - BILLING Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}",
  "message": "I need an invoice for order #67890"
}

### 7. Send Message - SUPPORT Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/messages
